div.p:
“6. The Death of Christ was attended by electric manifestations—by the darkness
                    over the land during the Crucifixion; the tearing of the temple veil in twain;
                    and the earthquake which finally ensued.

“Ivan regrets he cannot dine with us to-day,” he said, glancing at his sister;
                    “he is otherwise engaged. He says, however, that he hopes to have the pleasure
                    of looking in during the latter part of the evening.”
